"""Test get_backend_director_stats."""
response = self.perf.get_backend_director_stats(director_id=self.p_data.
    fe_port_id, metrics=pc.KPI, start_time=self.time_now, end_time=self.
    time_now)
self.assertIsInstance(response, dict)
self.assertEqual(response.get('reporting_level'), self.common.
    convert_to_snake_case(pc.BE_DIR))
